STARTING A NEW PROJECT
  1. genie init                    # Set up Genie
  2. genie spawn "Build MVP"       # Create first process
  3. genie fork "User Auth"        # Add a thread
  4. genie exec                    # Start working

DAILY WORKFLOW
  1. genie status                  # See where you left off
  2. genie exec                    # Resume or start next instruction
  3. genie yield                   # Pause when done for the day

HANDLING A BUG
  1. genie interrupt "Login broken on Safari"
  2. Select priority: [!] Critical
  3. genie exec                    # Fix is now next in queue

COMPLETING A PROCESS
  1. genie exec                    # Complete remaining instructions
  2. genie status                  # Verify all done
  3. genie archive auth_20251227   # Archive completed work

NAVIGATING BETWEEN WORK
  1. genie jump payments_20251229  # Switch to another process
  2. genie status                  # See new context
  3. genie exec                    # Work on new process

FIXING A MISTAKE
  1. genie rewind --last           # Undo last instruction
  2. genie exec                    # Re-implement differently
